\begin_layout Subsection
Delivering odorants: olfactometer design 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
There exists a variety of methods of deliverying odorants.
 Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "olfactometer-zoo"

\end_inset

 shows a sample of the zoo of olfactometers (devices for delivering odorants)
 that have been developed to deliver odorants in experimental preprarations.
 While the full assortment of olfactormeters is too rich to comprehensively
 survey here, all olfactometers can be classified into a few basic types
 based on: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout aEnumerate (ClassicThesis)
\begin_inset Flex CT - Spaced Low Small Caps
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
