\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 A valve is typically used to turn airstreams on or off.
 Is this valve upstream or downstream of the odorant? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout aEnumerate (ClassicThesis)
\begin_inset Flex CT - Spaced Low Small Caps
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
